The above will create the following layout:

| Index | `LView`                                  | `TView.data`
| ----: | ------------                                 | -------------
| `HEADER`
| `CONSTS`
| 10    | `[<child>, ...]`                             | `{type: Element, index: 10, parent: null, expandoIndex: 11, directivesIndex: 19, providersIndex: 20, viewProvidersIndex: 22, expandoEnd: 23}`
| `VARS`
